      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That's a good start, but it's a bit too generic. I need it to be more specific about the \"radicalism\" part to really get the crowd fired up. Can you add some sections that specifically call out how these progressive policies are attacking the nuclear family and undermining parental rights in schools? Make it feel like there's an urgent threat we need to fight against.",
